Menu Commander

Usage:
  menu [CONFIG --dry --loop]
  menu (-h|--help|--version)

Options:
  -d --dry
    Dry run - do not execute the command at the end, just show it

  -l --loop
    Reopen the menu after executing the selected command

  --version
    Show version number

  -h --help
    Show this help

Parameters:
  CONFIG
    The name of the menu config file without the .yml extension [default: menu]

Examples:
  menu --dry
  menu production --loop
  menu -ld
